+ What's This?

This is the Cleaning Services theme by [[*user winkwonkboi]], made for articles that pertain to the //Cleanliness Guaranteed*// (soon-to-be) canon.

To implement this theme, simply paste the following code at the top of your page:

[[div class="code"]]
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]@@
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:cleaning-services]]@@
[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[collapsible show="+ You see the 'Cleaning Services Theme' title?" hide="- Want to change it?"]]
Only optional, but if you like to switch the font of the top of your page, you can use the code below:

[[div class="code"]]
@@[[module CSS]]@@
@@#page-title {@@
@@    font-family: var(--header-font);@@
@@}@@
@@[[/module]]@@
[[/div]]

This changes it to the font you see for the 'SAFE CLEANUP PROFESSIONALS' title up above.
[[/collapsible]]

//Note: As this is a Black Highlighter based theme, the Black Highlighter theme should be used in conjunction for this theme to work. To learn more, go [[[theme:black-highlighter-theme|here.]]]//

